name: Alex Johnson
values: Passionate about social justice and environmental sustainability
interests: Hiking, rock climbing, playing guitar, reading, coding
summary:
Alex Johnson is a 30-year-old non-binary software developer based in Los Angeles, California. They are originally from Seattle, Washington. Alex attended Stanford University and speaks three languages - English, Spanish, and Mandarin. They are passionate about social justice and environmental sustainability, and their interests include hiking, rock climbing, playing guitar, reading, and coding. 

Identifying as agnostic and politically liberal, Alex is interested in a long-term relationship but is open to short ones too. They believe in monogamy and are interested in having children someday despite not having any currently. Their ethnicity is Hispanic/Latino and they're an Aquarius as per the zodiac. They identify as an INFP in the MBTI personality type.

Alex has a cat and a fish as pets. They drink occasionally but are not smokers or drug users. Being actively engaged in physical activities, Alex anticipates their partner to also lead an active life and prefer them to lead a non-smoking lifestyle and have no children, although they're open to those who want children.
